xubamp (0.2.0-1) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Visualization preferences match the original Winamp 2.9x dialog
    exactly: layout, wording, fps-labelled refresh slider, and
    Slow/Fast falloff sliders.
  * The playback stream requests 512-frame quanta so the analyzer and
    oscilloscope receive fresh audio every frame; combined with the
    ported classic falloff physics this restores the original dancing
    speed.
  * Playlist totals over an hour read H:MM:SS, never overflow the
    bottom bar, and the bitmap font gained the missing '/' glyph.

 -- Hector Oviedo <hector.ernesto.oviedo@gmail.com>  Wed, 16 Jul 2026 22:00:00 +0000

